properties.Name: SoftwareLicenseAgreement

Columns.Name: ContractId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Contract.

Columns.Name: SoftwareName
Columns.Description: The name of the software to be licensed.

Columns.Name: LicenseSection
Columns.Description: This section assigned the Licensee a specific type of license of specified duration in a specific geography(s).

Columns.Name: RestrictionsSection
Columns.Description:
This section specifies the restrictions on the Licensee to use the software.

Examples:

-  Copying the software
-  Transferring the software
-  Using the software on a network

Columns.Name: FeesSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies the license fees that are paid to the Licensor/Developer.

Columns.Name: FeesAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of fees paid to the Licensor/Developer.

Columns.Name: TitleSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies who has title to the software.

Columns.Name: WarrantySection
Columns.Description:
This section specifies the limited warranty applicable to the software:

(1)  The time period applicable

(2)  The media warranty upon which the software is supplied

Columns.Name: WarrantyDisclaimerSection
Columns.Description:
This section specifies the specific warranties that the Licensor/Developer is responsible for.

Implied warranties may not be disclaimed.

Columns.Name: WarrantyPeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The warranty period starting date.

Columns.Name: WarrantyPeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The warranty period ending date.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies the maintenance that is provided or available for the software.

Columns.Name: MaintenancePeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The maintenance period starting date.

Columns.Name: MaintenancePeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The maintenance period ending date.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceFeeAmount
Columns.Description: The fees for maintenance for the associated Maintenance Period.

Columns.Name: PaymentSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies the license fee payment terms.

Columns.Name: TaxesSection
Columns.Description: This section identifies who is responsible for state, sales, property and use taxes.

Columns.Name: LiabilitySection
Columns.Description: This section specifies the limitation of liability for the software.

Columns.Name: GoverningLawSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies the state whose laws will be used to interpret or enforce the contract.

Columns.Name: AssignmentDeclarationSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies the ability of the Licensee to transfer the contract to another person or legal entity.

Columns.Name: FinalAgreementSection
Columns.Description: This section specifies that this contract is the total and final agreement between the parties and it supersedes any prior discussions or correspondence.

Columns.Name: SeverabilitySection
Columns.Description: This section indicates that if a specific section is ruled or deemed unenforceable, then the other sections will remain in force. Warranty Disclaimer Section
